Malaysia. Sarawak: Kapit Division, Batang Baleh, Nanga Serani, 500 m elev., 4 May 1991, Runi et al. S.63137 (holotype: K [K000566618]!; isotypes: KEP [KEP43526, image seen]!, L [L3908632]!, SAN! [image seen], SAR 
